epair status" link:** https://www.asus.com/support/ (or https://www.asus.com/support/rma-location/ – both show the same link).\n\n**Conclusion:** The current public ASUS support pages do not provide a visible input field for checking repair status. Further navigation (such as region selection or account login) may be required, which was not reachable within the constraints of this task.', 'success': False, 'files_to_display': []}, 'interacted_element': None}])
